    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Sariguna Primatirta Tbk, together with its subsidiaries, produces and sells bottled drinking water products in Indonesia. The company operates through the Bottle, Non-Bottle, and Others segments. The company also has wholesale trading of food and beverages and the production and distribution of ice for food, beverage, and other uses. It sells drinking water under the Cleo, Super O2, VIO, Cleo Plantine, Anda, and S-Tube brands; and green tea under the NOGU brand. The company was formerly known as PT Sari Guna and changed its name to PT Sariguna Primatirta Tbk in December 1988. The company was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Sidoarjo, Indonesia. PT Sariguna Primatirta Tbk operates as a asubsidiary of PT Tancorp Global Abadi.",
